wikipedia_page.main: Flora Bramley (24 September 1904 – 23 June 1993) was an American-based English actress and comedian.

response: The Dude Cowboy is a 1926 American Western film directed by Jack Nelson and written by Paul M. Bryan. The film stars Bob Custer, Flora Bramley, Billy Bletcher, Howard Truesdale, Bruce Gordon and Amber Norman. The film was released on October 31, 1926, by Film Booking Offices of America.
